video_info.title: Josh Shapiro gives rousing speech in Philadelphia at rally for Kamala Harris and Tim Walz
video_info.description:
FULL SPEECH: Pennsylvania Gov. Josh Shapiro delivers a passionate speech in Philadelphia on Aug. 6, 2024 before introducing Vice President Kamala Harris and her running mate, Minnesota Gov. Tim Walz.
